(1, '5f890c6e-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Premium Wireless Headphones', 'Premium audio experience', 'Experience superior sound quality with our Premium Wireless Headphones featuring advanced active noise cancellation technology that blocks out ambient noise for an immersive listening experience. These headphones deliver crystal-clear audio with deep bass and crisp highs, perfect for music lovers and audiophiles. With an impressive 30-hour battery life, you can enjoy uninterrupted listening throughout your day without worrying about recharging. The comfortable over-ear design with soft cushioned ear cups ensures all-day comfort, while Bluetooth 5.0 connectivity provides seamless pairing with all your devices. Built-in controls allow easy volume adjustment and track selection. The foldable design makes them perfect for travel, and the included carrying case protects your investment.', '2026-01-23 14:32:41', '2026-01-23 14:32:41'),
