(48, '80e4c4f0-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Portable Charger 20000mAh', 'Never run out of power', 'Never worry about a dead battery again with our high-capacity 20000mAh Portable Charger that provides multiple full charges for your smartphones, tablets, and other USB devices. This powerful power bank features advanced fast-charging technology that delivers optimal charging speed for each connected device, getting you back to full battery up to 3 times faster than standard chargers. Dual USB output ports allow simultaneous charging of two devices, perfect for sharing with friends or powering multiple gadgets. The intelligent LED display shows remaining battery percentage so you always know when it\'s time to recharge. Built-in safety features protect against overcharging, overheating, and short circuits. The compact, portable design easily fits in bags or pockets, making it ideal for travel, commuting, camping, or emergency backup power. Compatible with all USB-charging devices.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(49, '80e54a6a-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Indoor Plant Pot Set', 'Beautify your space', 'Bring life and natural beauty into your home with our Indoor Plant Pot Set featuring three elegant ceramic pots in complementary sizes perfect for creating stunning plant displays. Each handcrafted pot showcases a timeless design that enhances any interior decor from modern minimalist to classic traditional. The essential drainage holes in each pot prevent waterlogging and root rot, promoting healthy plant growth, while the included matching saucers protect your furniture from water damage. The smooth glazed finish is easy to clean and resistant to staining. Ideal for herbs, succulents, small flowers, or decorative foliage, these versatile pots work beautifully on windowsills, shelves, desks, or as a cohesive centerpiece arrangement. The neutral color palette complements any color scheme while the durable ceramic construction ensures years of use. Perfect for plant enthusiasts or as a thoughtful gift.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(50, '80e5cc95-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Protein Powder Chocolate', 'Fuel your fitness', 'Power your workouts and recovery with our premium Whey Protein Powder in rich chocolate flavor that delivers 25 grams of high-quality protein per serving to support muscle growth and repair. This advanced formula uses fast-absorbing whey protein concentrate and isolate blend that your body can quickly utilize after intense training sessions. Each serving contains essential amino acids including BCAAs that are crucial for muscle protein synthesis and reducing exercise-induced muscle damage. The indulgent chocolate taste mixes smoothly without clumps in water, milk, or your favorite smoothie recipes, making post-workout nutrition something to look forward to. Low in sugar and fat while providing excellent nutritional value, this protein powder supports your fitness goals whether you\'re building muscle, losing weight, or maintaining a healthy lifestyle. Third-party tested for quality and purity.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(51, '80e64d84-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Hardcover Journal', 'Capture your thoughts', 'Preserve your thoughts, dreams, and daily experiences in our Premium Hardcover Journal featuring high-quality construction that stands up to frequent use. This beautifully designed journal contains 200 lined pages made from thick, smooth paper that prevents ink bleed-through, making it perfect for fountain pens, gel pens, or pencils. The durable hardcover protects your writing while the lay-flat binding allows comfortable writing from the first page to the last without the book closing on you. An elastic closure band keeps your journal securely shut and protects your privacy, while the built-in ribbon bookmark helps you quickly find your place. The compact size fits easily in bags and backpacks for writing on the go. Perfect for journaling, goal setting, creative writing, travel documentation, or as a gratitude journal. The elegant design makes it a thoughtful gift for writers, students, and reflective thinkers.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(52, '80e70ead-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Kitchen Knife Set', 'Essential kitchen tools', 'Elevate your culinary skills with our professional-grade Kitchen Knife Set featuring eight precision-forged knives that handle every cutting task from delicate slicing to heavy chopping. This comprehensive collection includes a chef\'s knife, bread knife, carving knife, utility knife, paring knife, kitchen shears, knife sharpener, and a beautiful wooden storage block. Each blade is crafted from high-carbon stainless steel that maintains its razor-sharp edge through countless uses while resisting rust, corrosion, and discoloration. The ergonomically designed handles provide comfortable grip and excellent control, reducing hand fatigue during extended prep work. The full tang construction ensures perfect balance and durability. The included knife sharpener keeps your blades performing at their peak, while the elegant wooden block stores and displays your knives safely within easy reach. Perfect for home chefs and cooking enthusiasts.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(53, '80e79076-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Fleece Blanket Queen', 'Cozy comfort', 'Wrap yourself in warmth and comfort with our ultra-soft Fleece Blanket in queen size that transforms your bed or couch into a cozy haven. This luxurious blanket is crafted from premium microfiber fleece that feels incredibly soft against your skin while providing exceptional warmth without excessive weight. The generous queen dimensions provide ample coverage for sharing or wrapping yourself completely. Unlike traditional blankets that pill and shed, our high-quality fleece maintains its smooth texture and vibrant color even after repeated washing. Machine washable and dryer safe for easy care and maintenance, this blanket becomes even softer with each wash. Perfect for movie nights, reading in bed, outdoor events, or adding an extra layer of warmth on cold nights. The versatile design complements any bedroom or living room decor. Lightweight enough for year-round use yet warm enough for winter comfort.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(54, '80e813c9-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Sunglasses Polarized', 'Protect your eyes', 'Shield your eyes in style with our Polarized Sunglasses featuring advanced UV400 lens technology that blocks 100% of harmful UVA and UVB rays while reducing glare from reflective surfaces. The polarized lenses dramatically improve visual clarity and reduce eye strain, making them perfect for driving, water sports, skiing, or any outdoor activities. Constructed with durable lightweight frames that withstand daily wear and active lifestyles, these sunglasses combine fashion with function. The scratch-resistant coating protects your lenses from damage, ensuring long-lasting clarity. The comfortable nose pads and temple tips provide a secure fit that stays in place during movement without pinching or slipping. Each pair comes with a protective hard case and cleaning cloth to keep your sunglasses in pristine condition. The timeless design suits all face shapes and complements any outfit from casual to sophisticated.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(55, '80e8cd1b-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Air Fryer 5.8 Quart', 'Healthier frying', 'Revolutionize your cooking with our Digital Air Fryer that uses rapid air circulation technology to create crispy, delicious meals with up to 85% less fat than traditional deep frying. The spacious 5.8-quart capacity accommodates whole chickens, multiple servings of wings, or large batches of french fries, making it perfect for families or entertaining. Eight preset cooking programs take the guesswork out of preparing favorites like chicken, steak, fish, vegetables, and desserts with one-touch convenience. The intuitive digital touchscreen allows precise temperature control from 180°F to 400°F and cooking times up to 60 minutes. The non-stick basket and separator are dishwasher safe for effortless cleanup. The cool-touch exterior and automatic shutoff ensure safe operation. Enjoy guilt-free fried foods that taste amazing while supporting your health goals. Includes recipe book with delicious meal ideas.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(56, '80e95397-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Gaming Mouse RGB', 'Level up your game', 'Dominate your competition with our high-performance Gaming Mouse featuring an advanced optical sensor with adjustable DPI up to 16,000 for pixel-precise accuracy and lightning-fast response times. This competitive-grade mouse is engineered for serious gamers who demand every advantage. Six programmable buttons can be customized with macros and complex commands through the intuitive software, giving you instant access to critical game functions. The customizable RGB lighting system offers millions of color combinations and dynamic effects that sync with your gaming setup. The ergonomic design with textured side grips ensures comfortable control during marathon gaming sessions while reducing hand fatigue. The ultra-durable switches are rated for 50 million clicks, and the braided cable prevents tangling and fraying. Onboard memory stores your profiles for consistent performance across different systems. Perfect for FPS, MOBA, MMO, and all competitive gaming.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(57, '80e9d698-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Dumbbell Set Adjustable', 'Complete home gym', 'Transform any space into a complete home gym with our Adjustable Dumbbell Set that replaces 15 sets of traditional dumbbells while occupying minimal space. This innovative system allows rapid weight adjustment from 5 to 52.5 pounds per dumbbell with a simple turn of the dial, eliminating the need to manually change plates between exercises. Perfect for progressive resistance training, you can seamlessly increase weight as you build strength without interrupting your workout flow. The compact storage tray keeps your dumbbells organized and protects your floors when not in use. The durable construction features a combination of metal and high-impact plastic components engineered for longevity. Suitable for all fitness levels from beginners to advanced athletes, these dumbbells support hundreds of exercises targeting every muscle group. Save money and space while achieving your strength training goals with professional-quality equipment in the comfort of your home.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(58, '80ea597e-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Wall Art Canvas Set', 'Elevate your decor', 'Transform your living space with our stunning Wall Art Canvas Set featuring three coordinated panels that create a captivating focal point in any room. This modern abstract design brings sophistication and visual interest to your walls while complementing contemporary, minimalist, and transitional decor styles. Each canvas is professionally stretched over solid wooden frames that prevent warping and sagging, ensuring your artwork maintains its pristine appearance for years. The high-resolution printing process delivers vibrant colors and sharp details that capture every nuance of the original artwork. Pre-installed hanging hardware makes installation effortless, and the gallery-wrapped edges create a polished, frameless look that appears to float on your wall. Perfect for living rooms, bedrooms, offices, or dining areas, this versatile art set instantly elevates your interior design. The three-panel configuration allows creative arrangement options to suit your space perfectly.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(59, '80eadb4b-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Mechanical Keyboard', 'Tactile typing experience', 'Experience superior typing performance with our RGB Mechanical Keyboard featuring genuine blue mechanical switches that deliver satisfying tactile feedback and an audible click with each keystroke. These premium switches are engineered for longevity with a 50-million keystroke lifespan while providing consistent actuation force and response. The full-size layout includes a number pad and dedicated media controls for convenient functionality. The aircraft-grade aluminum frame provides exceptional durability and stability that prevents keyboard flex during intense typing or gaming sessions. Customizable per-key RGB backlighting offers millions of color combinations and dynamic lighting effects controlled through intuitive software. The double-shot PBT keycaps resist shine and wear while maintaining their legends indefinitely. Anti-ghosting and N-key rollover ensure every keystroke registers accurately during rapid typing or complex gaming inputs. The braided USB cable and gold-plated connector ensure reliable connectivity. Perfect for programmers, writers, and gamers.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(60, '80eb6413-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Insulated Lunch Box', 'Fresh meals on the go', 'Keep your meals fresh and delicious throughout the day with our Insulated Lunch Box featuring advanced thermal insulation that maintains food temperature for hours whether hot or cold. This practical lunch solution includes multiple compartments that separate different foods, preventing flavors from mixing while keeping wet and dry items apart. The leakproof design uses secure zippered closures and sealed compartments that contain spills, making it safe to pack in bags without worry. Made from food-grade, BPA-free materials that are safe for your health and the environment. The included utensil set stores conveniently in a dedicated pocket, ensuring you\'re always prepared for meals. The adjustable shoulder strap and comfortable handle offer versatile carrying options for commuting, work, school, or outdoor activities. Easy to clean with a simple wipe-down, this lunch box promotes healthy eating habits by encouraging home-prepared meals while reducing waste from disposable packaging.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(61, '80ebe8f2-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Resistance Bands Set', 'Versatile workout tool', 'Achieve a complete full-body workout anywhere with our Resistance Bands Set featuring five color-coded bands offering progressive resistance levels from light to extra heavy. This versatile fitness system enables hundreds of exercises targeting every major muscle group for strength training, rehabilitation, flexibility, and toning without expensive gym equipment or weights. The premium latex construction provides smooth, consistent resistance that won\'t snap or lose elasticity with regular use. Comfortable foam handles prevent slipping and reduce hand fatigue during intense workouts, while the door anchor allows secure attachment for door-based exercises. The ankle straps enable lower body exercises with proper form and control. Compact and lightweight, these bands fit easily in luggage or bags, making them perfect for home workouts, travel, or outdoor training. Suitable for all fitness levels with included exercise guide showing proper techniques and workout routines.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
(62, '80ec6e42-f868-11f0-a10b-00163e1efc06', 'Floor Lamp Modern', 'Modern lighting solution', 'Illuminate your space with contemporary style using our Modern Floor Lamp that combines sleek design with practical functionality. This striking lamp features an adjustable head that pivots and tilts, allowing you to direct light precisely where needed for reading, working, or ambient lighting. The slim profile and minimalist aesthetic complement modern, industrial, and Scandinavian decor while the stable weighted base ensures it won\'t tip over. Energy-efficient LED technology provides bright, warm illumination that\'s easy on the eyes while consuming minimal electricity and eliminating the need for frequent bulb replacements. The convenient foot switch allows easy on/off control without bending down, perfect for bedside use. The durable metal construction ensures years of reliable performance. Ideal placement beside sofas, chairs, or beds creates the perfect reading nook while adding architectural interest to your room. Easy assembly with all necessary hardware included.', '2026-01-23 14:33:37', '2026-01-23 14:33:37'),
